    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       这是一个人类和魔物共存的世界，一直以来人类和魔物和平相处，互不干扰各自的生存空间。然而在某一天，魔物变得狂躁，无缘无故袭击了在野外活动的人类。玩家身为布拉诺伊保卫团团长受镇长之命去调查这一事件的缘由，因保卫团里的团员都要在城里戒备，防止魔物入侵，所以玩家需要另外招募各路勇士来组建一支属于自己的战斗团队。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>挑战BOSS，秀出操作</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249790/extras/4c49609888df34cccf06d0b3b231ff1e.avif?t=1728889164\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249790/extras_big/4c49609888df34cccf06d0b3b231ff1e.avif?t=1728889164 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >         游戏最核心的玩法是挑战野外BOSS，而挑战BOSS需要玩家切换角色进行走位布局，以减少BOSS对团队的伤害。职业的搭配和精妙的操作是成功击杀BOSS的关键。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>众多角色，自由搭配</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249790/extras/f596b9771532f1920f49a1361852ead4.avif?t=1728889164\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249790/extras_big/f596b9771532f1920f49a1361852ead4.avif?t=1728889164 width=800 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       小小勇士团中一共有25位角色，分5个职业，每个职业拥有两个技能。玩家可以按照自己的喜好和角色的技能搭配组建一支强力的队伍进行作战。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>收集材料，合成装备</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249790/extras/d9322b9624d3ce56a13e52776c328799.avif?t=1728889164\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249790/extras_big/d9322b9624d3ce56a13e52776c328799.avif?t=1728889164 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       游戏中每位角色最多可以佩戴6种装备，每种装备分了5个品质。在野外击杀魔物获得材料，材料用于合成装备。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>有趣解谜，充满挑战</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249790/extras/fb9967250d630cadc01135966a0b7e9b.avif?t=1728889164\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249790/extras_big/fb9967250d630cadc01135966a0b7e9b.avif?t=1728889164 width=800 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       剧情中会添加一些解谜玩法，让游戏增添几分色彩，避免一味地战斗让玩家觉得枯燥。解谜有一定的难度，若玩家最终不能解决，可进交流群或在评论中寻求帮助。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>激情对战，尽显策略</strong>      </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249790/extras/b5c71fb37e893d90c9a47c2560475798.avif?t=1728889164\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249790/extras_big/b5c71fb37e893d90c9a47c2560475798.avif?t=1728889164 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       游戏还设计了充满挑战的训练场，与另一支队伍进行对战。训练场包含了简单、普通、困难、噩梦4个难度，每次挑战都会随机生成不同的队伍，玩家能充分感受不同队伍的对战体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       游戏目前发布的是单机版本，后续我们会更新联网功能，届时会新增玩家对战、世界聊天、工会等玩法，敬请期待</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方交流群：Q群号891821082（小小勇士交流会）</p>",
